---
---

<section class="about" id="about" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-left">
        <p class="section-label" data-animate>About</p>
        <h2 class="section-heading" id="about-heading" data-animate data-delay="1">
          Built for the<br />work that matters.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="about-right">
        <div class="about-body" data-animate data-delay="2">
          <p>
            I spent years at Apple and Nike learning that strong digital work isn't just about how it looks — it's about how clearly it works, how well it performs, and how confidently it moves from idea to launch.
          </p>
          <p>
            At Apple, I worked on experiences shaped by performance, accessibility, and precision at scale. At Nike, I saw how brand, storytelling, and digital execution create momentum. That foundation shapes everything I do today.
          </p>
          <p>
            Now I work independently with founders, small businesses, and organizations who want high-quality results without the overhead of an agency. I bring strategy, design, development, and project management together — so projects don't stall between concept and execution.
          </p>
        </div>

        <dl class="about-stats" data-animate data-delay="3">
          <div class="stat">
            <dt class="stat-label">Experience</dt>
            <dd class="stat-value">10+ years</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <dt class="stat-label">Projects shipped</dt>
            <dd class="stat-value">50+</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <dt class="stat-label">Focus</dt>
            <dd class="stat-value">Web, brand &amp; digital products</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <dt class="stat-label">Location</dt>
            <dd class="stat-value">Hawaii / Remote</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: var(--c-bg-subtle);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-border);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-left {
    position: sticky;
    top: 100px;
  }

  .about-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-body p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
  }

  .about-body p:first-child {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--c-text);
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-border);
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--c-text);
  }

  @media (max-width: 840px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .about-left {
      position: static;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
